span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事關香港歷史之重大變局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想借大家少少位用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家可以原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOPvJL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOPvJL6.png&h=344452d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止惡法！為時未晚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意返由於預計示威人數好多，民陣已經將起點改咗喺維園！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百國聯軍助陣！感謝海外港人為香港人嘅未來而作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG0SmhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG0SmhW.png&h=5d5fe630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>愛因斯坦 (Albert Einstein)：「The world will not be destoryed by those who do evil, but by these who watch them without doing anything.(這個世界不會被那些作惡多端的人毀滅，而是冷眼旁觀、選擇保持緘默的人)」；鄭有傑(導演):「良心的沉默是邪惡的幫兇。」<br />\n<br />\n好多時歷史中嘅轉折位都係由表面上微不足道嘅小事/小人物而形成嘅，所以我地更加唔可以睇小自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=1695220c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全球聯署、白宮聯署、學界、各行各業、宗教、地區/ 海外港人等等）反送中聯署合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY%2Fhtmlview&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=e3faee2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview</a>"},{"pid":"455ff38433935bf7cc5262ed0f53001f68081a49","tid":1189401,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"赤化香港 2019"},{"pid":"55429f5812c47358d12f4685cca23d40a6e04a9c","tid":1189401,"uid":100772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T19:04:35.000Z","msg":"青山開放日"},{"pid":"3704831fbaa6d079ad747046f32b7b0539d096e3","tid":1189401,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T19:06:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}